      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of practical value, this vehicle is a straightforward option for anyone seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a solid opportunity for a buyer who appreciates honest condition and strong value. A smart pick for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone needing an inexpensive vehicle without unnecessary frills.",
