    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a dependable backup to have around. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, it\u2019s a great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just want inexpensive motoring, this one is well worth a look.",
