      "description": "Solid budget-minded project or backup driver with a strong-running engine, automatic transmission that engages as it should, and a chassis that feels fundamentally usable. It shows its age cosmetically and needs finishing work, but the core mechanical package has good bones and makes a great candidate for someone who wants dependable transportation with room to improve over time. A practical buy for an enthusiast, commuter, or DIY owner looking for value without paying premium-market money.",
