      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still feels ready for one more chapter. It\u2019s a budget-friendly ride with plenty of personality, ideal for someone who appreciates a practical set of wheels, a project with promise, or a dependable companion for short trips and everyday errands. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that makes it easy to picture in a driveway, on a back road, or serving as a handy extra vehicle when you need one. If you\u2019re looking for something inexpensive, useful, and full of potential, this one is easy to root for.",
      "price": 4900.0,
